{"tid":1487344,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"妍雨消失MOMOLAND活動 時隔2月「真實原因曝光」網心疼","createTime":"2019-08-19T08:32:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T03:44:34.000Z","uid":74065,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"3e328aeb05431b0aaa3dc8c8df575ed6fd533e2a","tid":1487344,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T08:32:26.000Z","msg":"南韓偶像妍雨（연우）今年23歲，6月的時候突然大量缺席團體MOMOLAND活動，因此傳出了退團消息，值得慶幸的是經紀公司否認，但19日時被曝光當時會這樣的真正原因，叫粉絲心疼。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4314/d4314854.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4314%2Fd4314854.jpg&h=7bb1a1b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲妍雨先前瘋傳要退出MOMOLAND。（圖／翻攝自MOMOLAND臉書）<br />\n<br />\n妍雨跑MOMOLAND團體行程時都會看網友討論，但面對惡評心裡承受龐大壓力導致一天比一天不安，最後罹患恐慌症，這就是為什麼她明明已經過了戲劇《綠豆餅》（意譯，녹두전）的試鏡卻突然退出的原因。<br />\n<br />\n消失於MOMOLAND團體活動，於官方CAFE上傳的文章接連刪除，並不是過去外界所猜測的退團，而是妍雨為了恐慌症的痊癒而休息，固定接受治療和排解心情後現在已經克服。所屬經紀公司MLD娛樂透露：「妍雨完成治療後將拍攝tvN戲劇《Cheap Cheonlima Mart》，希望大家多多支持。」"},{"pid":"531f0d5538a4dfd4df0d16bb0752cbb24098f9fe","tid":1487344,"uid":48577,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T08:33:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我陪伴她"},{"pid":"498257660549fdd09e1c6103e9383dd3e8fb17d1","tid":1487344,"uid":137470,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T08:35:47.000Z","msg":"惡評真係影響好多idol"},{"pid":"a49c9d0a7c6bce47c1187c72ccacf3a6e018f4f1","tid":1487344,"uid":7903,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T08:36:55.000Z","msg":"九成係俾啲日日嗌佢老婆既死毒撚嚇親<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b891ee8ace90815c442d9c59a6d819d9e61f710c","tid":1487344,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T08:46:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"